quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  106,1,(It is a great blessing and protection from Allah) for the safety of Quraish (caretaker of the house of Allah)
  106,2,for the safe passage (of their trade caravans) in winter and summer
  106,3,So let them worship the Lord of this house (the Ka’bah in Makkah)
  106,4,who provided them food against hunger and made them safe against fear
  107,1,Have you seen the one who denies the Day of Judgment
  107,2,It is he who drives away the orphan (harshly)
  107,3,and don’t encourage the feeding of the poor
  107,4,So woe to those who perform prayers (hypocrites)
  107,5,but are heedless of their prayer
  107,6,those who do good deeds only to be seen
  107,7,and they refuge (to share) small kindnesses
  108,1,"Surely, We have granted you (Muhammad) a river in Paradise (Kauther)"
  108,2,"Therefore, offer prayer to your Lord and sacrifice"
  108,3,"Surely, he who hates you (O Muhammad), he will be cut off (from good of both worlds)"